reviewText: Nobody buys a movie like this expecting a high-quality production. These movies are implausible and involve some tacky acting and situations, but as far as disaster movies go, they are a decent amount of fun. Don't expect realistic scenarios or a ton of character development or fleshed out plots. As far as destruction goes, there should be enough to make most disaster movie fans happy.

reviewText: The movies are good TV productions. However, I'm giving this product four stars because I caught part of 10.5 on TV and wanted to see the entire movie. I've never been disappointed with an Amazon purchase.
